name: MusicPlayer.PlaybackStatus
desc: The music player playback status modes.

items.name: static func == (MusicPlayer.PlaybackStatus, MusicPlayer.PlaybackStatus) -> Bool
items.desc: Returns a Boolean value indicating whether two values are equal.

items.name: case interrupted
items.desc: The music player is in an interrupted state, such as from an incoming phone call.

items.name: case paused
items.desc: The music player is in a paused state.

items.name: case seekingBackward
items.desc: The music player is seeking backward.

items.name: case seekingForward
items.desc: The music player is seeking forward.

items.name: case stopped
items.desc: The music player is in a stopped state.

items.name: func hash(into: inout Hasher)
items.desc: Hashes the essential components of this value by feeding them into the given hasher.
